reviewText: I understood that Hallmark sold good, clean, family movies. Not so. They have sold out to the almighty dollar, god of nudity and trashy behaviours.  These disks contain the above. If you are cobcerned with chastity and moral values/ethics these are not for you.
Gee, you must think I and everyone else are mindreaders, ya goose. How about giving us some info on what titles are in the collection, DUH !!
